  "description": "A component that connects to Moonshot AI's Kimi large language models for \nadvanced natural language processing. It enables text generation, long-context \nreasoning, summarization, and tool use. The Kimi K2 family offers a 256K context \nwindow with thinking and non-thinking modes and strong agentic performance, while \nthe classic Moonshot v1 models provide cost-effective options across 8K, 32K, and \n128K context sizes. The component is suitable for integrating intelligent \nreasoning and content generation into pipelines where long context and accuracy \nare key.",
